---
title: Zesty Beyond Meat® Bowls with Lime Aioli
description: Peppers, zucchini and Beyond Meat® are a match made in heaven! This dish capitalizes on this classic trio, with crispy roasted potatoes and a creamy lime aioli to top it all off. Altogether, it's the perfect, bright and punchy bowl!
